Servlet Adapter for Variant Java Client

Packages 
Package Description
com.variant.client.servlet
Servlet Adapter for the "bare" Variant Java Client, providing greatly simplified integration for host applications written on top of the Java Servlet API.
com.variant.client.servlet.impl
Private implementations of the interfaces in package com.variant.client.server
com.variant.client.servlet.util
Utility classes used throughout the servet adapter.
